{"tid":2166470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉華課程 普林斯頓准學生匿名","createTime":"2020-08-20T12:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T12:36:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b2c0e93d5400f71c67942ac54aecfcfcac92570","tid":2166470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:34:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/3NRTGHLZM5D27CX7C27ALENG2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F3NRTGHLZM5D27CX7C27ALENG2A%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=2331fcef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F3NRTGHLZM5D27CX7C27ALENG2A%2F&h=6d0fe191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/3NRTGHLZM5D27CX7C27ALENG2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n涉華課程 普林斯頓准學生匿名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OQfqB6KDpeobGfKtiQ2C6w07j_0=/1028x685/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5FS43PPDZVHTTDSGR6JISEY7BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOQfqB6KDpeobGfKtiQ2C6w07j_0%3D%2F1028x685%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5FS43PPDZVHTTDSGR6JISEY7BE.jpg&h=bed1c59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普林斯頓大學<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】北京在香港實施國安法，不單影響本港學術自由，亦蔓延到美國的大學，一些精英大學在秋季課程將加上警告標籤，提醒學生課程涉及中國政府認為是敏感的材料，各大學亦設法保護學生和教職員不被中國當局起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者憂網上授課被錄<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。說，「我們不能自我審查。如果我們中國科目教育社群出於恐懼，而停教天安門、新疆或任何中國政府不想我們討論的敏感課題，我們就輸了」，但為保護學生，課程將加警告和作業用代號。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。，一些學者擔心授課和討論會被錄下，並落入中國手上。<br />\n<br />\n麻省安默斯特學院就有教授正考慮匿名網上聊天，讓學生可自由發言。哈佛商學院工商管理碩士課程一些個案研究，涉新疆、港台等課題，亦擬准許擔心有風險的學生不參加這些政治敏感話題討論。"},{"pid":"5dbda4812bf923500e408bfffa460a0fdd6d42cf","tid":2166470,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會有中國留學生reg科攞料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}